---
// Features section for Portfolio AI landing page
---
<section class="py-20 bg-secondary/5" id="features">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center space-y-4 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">
        Powerful Features for Smart Investors
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Portfolio AI combines cutting-edge technology with intuitive design to give you 
        the tools you need to make better investment decisions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-card border-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-chart-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 17l6-6 4 4 8-8"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">Advanced Portfolio Tracking</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Monitor your investments with real-time data and comprehensive performance metrics across multiple asset classes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-chart-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">AI-Powered Insights</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Get personalized recommendations and market analysis powered by advanced machine learning algorithms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-chart-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">Interactive Charts & Analytics</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Visualize your data with beautiful, interactive charts and detailed analytics to make informed decisions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-chart-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">Bank-Level Security</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Your financial data is protected with enterprise-grade encryption and security protocols.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-chart-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">Real-Time Alerts</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Stay informed with instant notifications about market movements and portfolio changes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-chart-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 12l3-3 3 3 4-4M8 21l4-4 4 4M3 4h18M4 4h16v12a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">Goal Tracking</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Set and track your financial goals with AI-assisted planning and progress monitoring.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-chart-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">Mobile Optimized</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Access your portfolio anywhere with our responsive design and mobile-first approach.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-chart-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">Global Markets</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Track investments across international markets with multi-currency support.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-chart-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 17h5l-5 5l-5-5h5v-5a7.81 7.81 0 01-6-7.72c0-4.42 3.58-8 8-8s8 3.58 8 8A7.81 7.81 0 0115 12.28V17z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">Smart Notifications</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Receive intelligent alerts about opportunities and risks tailored to your investment style.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
